Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.28,0:00:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 这里是情报部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.78,0:00:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.45,0:00:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.82,0:00:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您可以把记忆传给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.98,0:00:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去哪就去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.44,0:00:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你玩得好像很开心呐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.57,0:00:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真调皮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.50,0:00:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么能让你窥视我记忆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.54,0:01:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裁决者必须得保持人偶的样子才行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是为了你的方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你又是什么目的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是可以改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.64,0:01:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是指拥有人类感情的裁决者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.15,0:01:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我们并不单单是人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.15,0:01:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荒唐 逗得我的花都缩回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.87,0:01:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都是人偶 包括我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该早就明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.46,0:01:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是从何而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.38,0:01:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些坠入虚无的人类的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.46,0:01:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就在其上面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.68,0:01:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要裁决者身上流着他们的血
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.35,0:01:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的无谓挣扎根本改变不了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.77,0:01:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裁决者采取的行动都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:01:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.27,0:02:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很快就会体会到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请带我到最底层
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 要去那种地方...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女孩也要带去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.26,0:02:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.11,0:02:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知幸 知幸...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的...房间？为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会 不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么快就醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\fs85\pos(959,962)}自杀之旅{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是您母亲做的人偶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手很巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里巧啦 根本就不像好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.50,0:03:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我一直视如珍宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你差点让我以为至今为止的事都是梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知幸小姐死后三个月的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我为您搭把手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 我一个人能走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.62,0:04:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我念念图书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真喜欢夏沃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知幸 我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她无法看到我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们无法与现世里的人对话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:05:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连碰也碰不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么不早告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么带我来这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您收下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.41,0:06:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带您来这里 并不是为了让您见到母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此时此刻 世界每1小时就有约7000人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人一生中不平之事居多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的生命享尽天年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有的生命转瞬即逝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人的生命...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所能换来的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便足以让知幸小姐在此时此地复活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.53,0:07:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按下这个按钮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样您在奎因德基姆一切记忆就会被消除
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转而复活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间已经不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请下决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要别人的生命交换？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会出现家人或朋友替我死的可能是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是 现在的世界人囗已超过了70亿人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,概率上来说是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您母亲 父亲 还有您的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有知道知幸小姐的人 都会被消除您死去的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈我呢 最喜欢看滑着冰的知幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还是看你成长得如此出色的样子 比什么都让我开心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.99,0:08:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是因为不能滑冰了而难过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人与人是不可能相互理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人追求相互理解是错误的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 这是你最爱吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈我啊 就是改不了做3人份的习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知幸 妈妈对不起你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候 我没能了解你的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈...失职了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我...连女儿的心情都理解不了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不...不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈好想你啊 知幸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...好想复活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复活之后我想和妈妈好好谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.73,0:09:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向她道歉....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信人追求理解并不是错误的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.08,0:09:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也还是希望能够互相理解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以别人的生命...交换...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能复活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是没办法的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你猜得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有其他喜欢的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你马上答应与我交往
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.01,0:10:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么简单的愿望 我都没能为她实现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:11:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我做什么都可以  让我回到孩子们的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还听到老婆感谢我的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我决定为了给受害者们报仇而活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你压住怒气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不想去你妹妹的身边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.33,0:11:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能有这一生 知足了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...下不了手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.34,0:11:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.47,0:11:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人...都有在乎的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.06,0:11:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他们都与知幸小姐不相干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我当然知道 就算如此...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是与我无关的人 肯定也有背后关心他们的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.62,0:11:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我妈妈那样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 我好想和妈妈说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我太不珍惜自己的生命了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我没能体谅妈妈的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你这么伤透了心 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能与你好好道别
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.66,0:13:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德基姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欺骗了您 实在是万分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.17,0:14:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还让您这么痛苦...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非这也是裁决的一环吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是悲伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德基姆...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想...更好的了解您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更加的理解您...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道...用这种方法...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个裁决者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...我...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都懂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德基姆...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对他动了什么手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是让他和人类一起裁决罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.06,0:15:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裁决者越是接近人类 越是难以做出裁定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还得要承受痛苦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.73,0:16:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类是无法审判人类的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你清楚 为何还这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算裁决会难产 也不是随便裁决人类的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界不能再保持这个样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么又有什么理由特地让裁决者们承受痛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裁决不伴随着痛苦 意义何在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意义？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛苦 挣扎...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.97,0:16:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活着不就是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活着？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「活着」这个词是有死亡的人才有资格用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.69,0:16:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连活也没活过 更不用说死过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算接进了人类 人偶还是人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.99,0:16:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都活在当下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是经过了审判 没有了灵魂的人偶们的废弃之处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本是禁止入内的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我也会来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.19,0:17:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类即便死去 也想努力活在当下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为那样的人类...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是值得尊敬的 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.53,0:17:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.20,0:17:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我耳朵都要听出茧子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茧子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.95,0:17:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 立场和平时反了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 要去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:18:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你对死亡情有独钟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知幸小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您觉得活着很幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想成为能让来到这里的客人说出这句话的裁决者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.47,0:18:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 就别板着这张脸嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能笑几个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像...像这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.27,0:18:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.40,0:18:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候自然就会笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我该道别了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 请您一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.07,0:19:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 弥麦恩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已经不会再回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我倒酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是来这干嘛的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管了 来喝几杯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:20:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 你家小子居然...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们今后该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明还有那么多裁决者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.65,0:20:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再让死者保留死亡记忆 送过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.78,0:20:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 还得观望一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们什么也不用做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似她被花头老爷子盯上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥 她怎么搞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她也只好乖乖的喽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 裁决者永远停止不了裁决
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为裁决就是他们的存在价值
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二 裁决者无法有死亡的经验
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.51,0:20:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为死亡会拉近他们与人类的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三 裁决者没有感情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.69,0:20:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他们是人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四 裁决者不得接近生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:21:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为会招致自身的毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临 这里是奎因德基姆
